      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can small churches use digital ads effectively?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Absolutely. Small churches often have an advantage because they can respond personally to every person who engages with an ad. Digital ads level the playing field, allowing a church of 50 to reach the same community as a megachurch. What matters most is your follow-up process, not your church size."
        }
